#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:9
msgid "Linux環境で行う初回作業"
msgstr "Initial tasks performed in a Linux environment"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:11
msgid ""
"新しくLinux環境を手に入れたとき、毎回行う作業があります。しかし、その作業内容を毎回調べ直すのは非効率です。本記事では、私が行っている初回セットアップと、その後の保守作業についてまとめました。主にUbuntuベースの環境を想定しています。"
msgstr ""
"There are certain tasks you must perform every time you get a new Linux "
"environment. However, it is inefficient to re-examine the work details every"
" time. In this article, I summarized the initial setup and subsequent "
"maintenance work that I did. Mainly assumes an Ubuntu-based environment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:18
msgid "rootユーザでの初期作業"
msgstr "Initial tasks as root user"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:20
msgid "最初に、rootユーザまたはsudo権限を持ったユーザで以下の作業を行います。"
msgstr ""
"First, perform the following steps as root user or a user with sudo "
"privileges."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:23
msgid "パッケージの更新"
msgstr "Package updates"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:30
msgid "基本ツールのインストール"
msgstr "Installing basic tools"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:32
msgid "開発や設定に必要な最低限のツールをインストールします。"
msgstr "Install the minimum tools required for development and configuration."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:39
msgid "日本語フォントのインストール"
msgstr "Installing Japanese fonts"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:41
msgid "日本語表示に必要なフォントをインストールします。"
msgstr "Install the fonts required for Japanese display."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:48
msgid "ロケール設定"
msgstr "Locale settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:50
msgid "日本語ロケールを設定します。"
msgstr "Set the Japanese locale."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:59
msgid "設定が反映されているか確認します。"
msgstr "Check whether the settings are reflected."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:65
msgid "出力の一部に以下が含まれていればOKです。"
msgstr "It is OK if part of the output contains the following:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:72
msgid "タイムゾーン設定"
msgstr "Time zone settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:74
msgid "JST（日本標準時）に設定します。"
msgstr "Set to JST (Japan Standard Time)."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:80
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:103
msgid "確認コマンド："
msgstr "Confirmation command:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:86
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:109
msgid "出力例："
msgstr "Example output:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:93
msgid "ファイアウォールの設定"
msgstr "Firewall settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:95
msgid "基本的なセキュリティ設定を行います。"
msgstr "Configure basic security settings."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:119
msgid "パッケージの定期メンテナンス"
msgstr "Regular package maintenance"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:121
msgid "`cron` で定期的に不要なパッケージの削除を行います。"
msgstr "Use `cron` to periodically remove unnecessary packages."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:130
msgid "作業用ユーザの追加と権限設定"
msgstr "Adding work users and setting permissions"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:132
msgid "作業用ユーザを作成し、sudo権限を付与します。"
msgstr "Create a working user and grant sudo privileges."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:140
msgid "ユーザでの初期作業"
msgstr "Initial work with users"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:142
msgid "ここからは、作成した作業用ユーザ（例: `your-username`）に切り替えて行います。"
msgstr ""
"From here, switch to the work user you created (e.g. `your-username`)."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:145
msgid "SSH公開鍵の設定"
msgstr "Configuring SSH public key"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:147
msgid "SSHでの接続に備えて、`.ssh/authorized_keys` に公開鍵を配置します。"
msgstr ""
"Place the public key in `.ssh/authorized_keys` in preparation for SSH "
"connection."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:157
msgid "接続確認"
msgstr "Connection confirmation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:159
msgid "別マシンからSSH接続できることを確認します。"
msgstr "Verify that you can connect via SSH from another machine."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:166
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-01-initial-setup-linux.rst:168
msgid ""
"この記事では、Linux環境で最初に行うべき基本的なセットアップ手順と、最低限のメンテナンスについてまとめました。毎回調べ直す手間を省くため、自分用のリファレンスとして活用していきます。必要に応じて随時更新予定です。"
msgstr ""
"This article summarizes the basic setup steps and minimum maintenance that "
"should be performed in a Linux environment. I will use it as my own "
"reference to save myself the trouble of having to look it up every time. It "
"will be updated from time to time as necessary."

